                     <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18171203-51-off260 t18171203-51-crimeloc262"></join>, three reams of paper, value 4l., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18171203-51-victim367" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Dutton
                     <interp inst="t18171203-51-victim367" type="surname" value="Dutton"></interp>
